    <briefdescription>
<para>HID hat switch handler. Declared at sketch scope for each hat switch. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Self-registers into a static linked list at construction. Dispatches to OsJoystick.setHat() with direction clamped to 0–8. </para>
